 Everything by me (doors, docs, etc) are copyrighted (c) GREMLiNS MAXsWARE
 Use this door at your own risk, it's provided as is... So don't blame me!

 Fluffy Net via the  BBS community is slowly dying  and I'd name a few who
 have caused this to happen,  but I s'pose who cares.. except a few of us!
 It's sad to see a great world network like Fluffy Net lose it's users and
 all that, but all things must and will come to an end.. that's life?! :-)

 @{b}1998:@{ub} Well, this has been an  eventful year with it's usual ups and downs
 whether it be job, home and relationship related  but I'm still alive and
 so is Zeffy, who's very good. The BBS is quieter these days but I'm still
 supporting the Amiga and MAXs (..and Fluffy) community, which I enjoy but
 not as much as the old days when the BBS was thriving, but all is well. I
 hope to be around a long while, till the HD dies anyways. Let's hope that
 1999 is a bigger and  better year, and that goes for everybody out there!
 Zeffy and I should hopefully  be travelling UK and Europe early 2000, not
 sure exactly what months but around March or earlier. We really want too!
 So we'll meet all you  Fluffy people in UK, if any of you still exist and
 all that, so should be fun.  Anyways, with all that said,  here's a small
 msg for you all....

 @{"   Zeffy and I wish everybody around the World all the best for 1999..   "}


 Now time to go and get pissed... "Burp!"

@endnode
